metadata.name: Saving NFT's from Destruction (Episode VI): AWOL
metadata.description:
In the near future, the Ethereum gas wars have created major conflict around the world. The United States Government have sent in a elite Seal Team  to prevent the threat of nuclear gas war. The mission Neptune Spear II has failed. Now,  Sgt. Sully has been tasked to stop the destruction of the blockchain at all cost, or die trying.


**Top Bidder will receive Episodes I-V Airdropped-minted on SuperRare // ***Bidders edition Episode I will be airdropped to each bidder on Episode VI auction.
